openmediavault-themekit (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial stable release of OpenMediaVault Themekit.
  * Added extensive collection of pre-configured themes (Catppuccin, Rose Pine, Gruvbox, Nord, Dracula, etc.).
  * Added dynamic styling engine with fallback variables to ensure uniform UI scaling across custom themes.
  * Fixed contrast issues for dropdowns, popover menus, and sidebar list items in both light and dark modes.
  * Implemented dynamic logo inversion for themes with lighter backgrounds.
  * Corrected active list item backgrounds and icon color inheritances for seamless integration with Angular Material UI.
  * Included Salt deploy modules and APT hooks to guarantee UI state persistence across system updates.
  * Developed Settings page for effortlessly toggling themes and accents.

 -- Saurabh Nakkarike <gradelabsin@gmail.com>  Sat, 11 Jul 2026 00:45:00 +0530
